{
  "stem": "3165.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my mother, again, at night, would go to every house-- to as many houses as she can, many villages far away, and come back at night and tell us we got to move again, go again, hide again.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then one evening, she went out again to look.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And like, she'd come back like, you know, during the night, like maybe 3:00, 4:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And here I woke up, it was early in the morning, maybe-- I don't know, maybe 5 or 6 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I saw-- we were all on the floor, and I sort of looked, and I-- I see my mother's not here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I thought, gee, it's-- it's morning already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "She should be here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She's not back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I don't know, I guess I fell asleep again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And sure enough, later that day, this lady, the woman of the house, she comes up to us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And now she tells me, she tells us, I have bad news for you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[SOBS] She said, last night, she says, your mother was looking for a place-- and it was snowing that night-- and I guess she saw the Ukrainian police following her.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And so she ran [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] down the snow on the fields.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And she saw up to-- saw a tree, and she went up to a tree, climbed up to a tree to hide.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And of course, this police followed her footsteps all the way to the tree.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they said that-- she said they took her down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they were torturing right there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "She said that they were taking needles in under her fingernails, pushed right through.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And they said, you must have more children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "You must have more children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "You have to tell us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And of course, she wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
